---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; URL=/maintenance" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="intro">
        <h1>예수님과 함께 걸어요 🌿</h1>
        <p>매일의 순간을 기록하고 나누는 공간에 오신 걸 환영합니다.</p>
        <p>작은 걸음 하나하나를 예수님과 함께 걸으며, 기록으로 남겨보세요.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="recent-journey">
        <h2>최근 여정</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/journey/first-post">처음 글: 내 믿음의 시작</a></li>
          <li><a href="/journey/second-post">두 번째 글: 감사의 기록</a></li>
          <li><a href="/journey/third-post">세 번째 글: 작은 기적들</a></li>
        </ul>
        <a class="more-link" href="/journey">모든 여정 보기 →</a>
      </section>

      <section class="verse">
        <blockquote>
          "내가 약할 그 때에 곧 강함이라." — 고린도후서 12:10
        </blockquote>
      </section>

      <section class="cta">
        <a href="/join" class="start-btn">🌟 함께 기록 시작하기</a>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .intro h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .intro p {
    margin: 0.3rem 0;
    color: #555;
  }
  .recent-journey h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .recent-journey ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .recent-journey li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  .recent-journey a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #4b6cb7;
  }
  .recent-journey a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .more-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #4b6cb7;
  }
  .verse blockquote {
    margin: 2rem auto;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #666;
  }
  .cta .start-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    background: #4b6cb7;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .cta .start-btn:hover {
    background: #3a539b;
  }
</style>
